## BRAINDRAIN environment variables (example)
##
## Copy to .env.dev or .env.prod and fill in your values.
## Server auto-loads .env.dev → .env.prod → .env (first found, non-overriding).
## DO NOT commit real secrets.

# Auto-set by install.sh. Override if you move the repo or use a custom launcher.
# BRAINDRAIN_LAUNCHER_PATH=/absolute/path/to/your/braindrain/config/braindrain

# Optional: override hub config location (default: config/hub_config.yaml next to server.py)
# BRAINDRAIN_CONFIG=/path/to/your/BRAIN_MCP_HUB/config/hub_config.yaml

# ── GitHub MCP (deferred tool) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_...

# ── Local LLM endpoints ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LM Studio (OpenAI-compatible, default port 1234)
# LMSTUDIO_BASE_URL=http://localhost:1234/v1
# LMSTUDIO_API_KEY=
# LMSTUDIO_EMBED_MODEL=text-embedding-3-small

# Ollama (default port 11434)
# OLLAMA_HOST=http://localhost:11434

# ── Cloud embeddings providers ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# OpenAI
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Google AI Studio (generous free tier)
# GOOGLE_AISTUDIO_API_KEY=...
# GOOGLE_AISTUDIO_BASE_URL=https://generativelanguage.googleapis.com/v1beta/openai/
# GOOGLE_AISTUDIO_EMBED_MODEL=text-embedding-004

# Hugging Face Inference
# HUGGINGFACE_API_KEY=hf_...
# HUGGINGFACE_BASE_URL=https://api-inference.huggingface.co
# HUGGINGFACE_EMBED_MODEL=sentence-transformers/all-MiniLM-L6-v2

# Mixedbread (embeddings + rerankers)
# MIXEDBREAD_API_KEY=...
# MIXEDBREAD_BASE_URL=https://api.mixedbread.ai/v1
# MIXEDBREAD_EMBED_MODEL=mxbai-embed-large-v1

# Groq
# GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# ── Optional tool wiring ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
# FileScopeMCP (build separately: https://github.com/admica/FileScopeMCP)
# FILESCOPE_MCP_SERVER_JS=/usr/local/bin/filescope-mcp-server.js
# FILESCOPE_BASE_DIR=.
